The paper discusses the collapse of boolean and polynomial hierarchies, which are central topics in computational complexity theory. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CC (Computational Complexity). The paper also involves techniques related to data structures (cs.DS), logic (cs.LO), cryptography (cs.CR), and information theory (cs.IT).
